HEADWORD: Mottled
<hw>Mot"tled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Motley</er>.]</ety> <def>Marked with spots of different colors;
variegated; spotted; <as>as, <ex>mottled</ex> wood</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>mottled</xex> meadows.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Drayton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

